data.description: DON’T MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY!!! *Motivated Sellers* This beautiful pool home boasts over 2400sqft of living space which includes a living room off the kitchen & a family room with formal dinning room. Large primary bedroom features his & her walk in closets & sliders going out to the pool. The spacious bathroom has double sinks, a garden tub & separate shower. Eat in kitchen with granite counters and stainless steel appliances. The oversized laundry room has lots of cabinets for extra storage space. Outside you’ll find a separate pool bath & large storage closet. Whole house reverse osmosis system, screened front entry. New Roof (2023). Newer A/C (2020) NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE!!
